s into mixing bowl and place Varoma back into position. Secure Varoma lid and cook <b>5 min\/Varoma\/\/speed 1<b> or until noodles are soft and vegetables are cooked to your liking. Meanwhile, remove edamame beans from pods and set aside. Discard pods."},{"content":"Divide steamed vegetables, edamame beans and ramen between serving bowls and discard the star anise. Serve garnished with spring onions\/shallots, sesame seeds and lime wedges."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Check the label of your noodles to ensure they are egg free.","Yasai translates to \"vegetable\" in Japanese."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","35m","4 portions"]}